  "overview" : "## Return Value\n\nReturns a pointer to the TOC buffer (do not deallocate).\n\n## Overview\n\nGet the full Table Of Contents.\n\nAll CDTOC fields passed across I\/O Kit APIs are guaranteed to be binary-encoded (no BCD-encoded numbers are ever passed).",
  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/iocdmedia\/1811363-gettoc\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T21:27:28Z\n---\n\n# getTOC\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvirtual CDTOC * getTOC(); \n```\n\n## Return Value\n\nReturns a pointer to the TOC buffer (do not deallocate).\n\n## Overview\n\nGet the full Table Of Contents.\n\nAll CDTOC fields passed across I\/O Kit APIs are guaranteed to be binary-encoded (no BCD-encoded numbers are ever passed).\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\n- **getSpeed**\n- **read**\n- **readCD()**\n- **readCD()**\n- **readDiscInfo**\n- **readISRC**\n- **readMCN**\n- **readTOC**\n- **readTrackInfo**\n- **setSpeed**\n\n",
